Package: clock
Title: Calendars, Time Points, and Durations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Davis",
             family = "Vaughan",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "davis@rstudio.com"),
      person(given = "RStudio",
             role = "cph"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive interface for date and datetime
    manipulations. Both naive and zoned datetimes are supported, with
    precision up to nanoseconds. Additionally, multiple types of calendars
    have been implemented, allowing for various ways to represent calendar
    dates, such as year-month-day, year-month-weekday, or
    year-quarter-day.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/DavisVaughan/clock
BugReports: https://github.com/DavisVaughan/clock/issues
